Package com.project.dao

Class NonVegItemsDaoImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.project.dao.NonVegItemsDaoImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NonVegItemsDao
    public class NonVegItemsDaoImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements NonVegItemsDao
    This class implements the NonVegItemsDao interface and defines all it's methods. The methods are for inserting, retrieving, modifying and deleting NonVegItems from the database for a particular diet plan. This class takes the help of SignUpUtility class to establish and close the connection with the database to perform the required operations.
    Author:
    Harsh Sharma
